    • verifyEligibilityToApply

      public Optional<String> verifyEligibilityToApply(User user, BTOProjectTypeID typeId)
      Check the eligibility of the user applying. Able to apply for a project cannot apply for multiple projects. - Singles, 35 years old and above, can ONLY apply for 2-Room - Married, 21 years old and above, can apply for any flat types (2- Room or 3-Room)
      Parameters:
      user - the applicant
      Returns:
      error message if the user cannot apply for a project type.
